01:03:06,574 --> 01:03:09,202
[ominous music playing]

1176
01:03:12,789 --> 01:03:16,542
But as I'm driving,
I feel myself slipping away.

1177
01:03:18,044 --> 01:03:20,838
Like my brain just detaching.

1178
01:03:23,674 --> 01:03:29,514
I ended up having an almost out-of-body
experience for, like, 24 hours.

1179
01:03:32,809 --> 01:03:36,103
And then when I come back out of the fog,

1180
01:03:36,187 --> 01:03:39,774
I am in… the middle of nowhere.

1181
01:03:39,857 --> 01:03:41,651
I have no idea where I am.

1182
01:03:42,902 --> 01:03:46,656
And… I have been picked up

1183
01:03:47,949 --> 01:03:52,286
by this Native American family
who found me wandering around.

1184
01:03:54,330 --> 01:03:56,415
And it turns out I was in Arizona.

1185
01:03:56,999 --> 01:04:00,127
And… they called

1186
01:04:00,211 --> 01:04:02,505
um, paramedics and the police,

1187
01:04:02,588 --> 01:04:04,841
and they take me to a hospital.

1188
01:04:04,924 --> 01:04:08,386
The doctor comes in to, um…

1189
01:04:09,554 --> 01:04:11,389
see me and he says, "You know,

1190
01:04:11,472 --> 01:04:14,267
this sounds like a dissociative episode."

1191
01:04:14,934 --> 01:04:20,523
And he tells me I have complex PTSD
from what I just went through with Ian.

1192
01:04:20,606 --> 01:04:22,817
[somber music playing]

1193
01:04:22,900 --> 01:04:23,734
So later,

1194
01:04:23,818 --> 01:04:27,029
after all this supposed cyberstalking,

1195
01:04:27,530 --> 01:04:29,282
when they arrested me,

1196
01:04:29,991 --> 01:04:33,077
they read through
these two emails that I sent.

1197
01:04:33,160 --> 01:04:34,871
[Cunha] "Get ready, the truth is coming."

1198
01:04:34,954 --> 01:04:37,874
"God's law is above all laws,
including the law of man."

1199
01:04:39,625 --> 01:04:41,127
So did you write this?

1200
01:04:41,627 --> 01:04:43,087
[Michelle] Yeah, that was me.

1201
01:04:44,380 --> 01:04:47,300
I'm not really sure how to explain to him.

1202
01:04:47,800 --> 01:04:50,303
I don't even really understand

1203
01:04:50,386 --> 01:04:54,473
where a lot of it came from
or why I wrote it.

1204
01:04:55,516 --> 01:04:57,727
I only ever sent these two emails.

1205
01:04:57,810 --> 01:04:58,811
[chimes]

1206
01:04:58,895 --> 01:05:03,024
But I was framed
for all this horrible cyberstalking.

1207
01:05:03,900 --> 01:05:06,527
-[dogs barking]
-[tires screech]

1208
01:05:06,611 --> 01:05:07,778
[car engine revs]

1209
01:05:07,862 --> 01:05:11,490
Michelle's story does sound crazy,

1210
01:05:11,574 --> 01:05:13,784
that she had, effectively,
a nervous breakdown.

1211
01:05:15,703 --> 01:05:17,496
[Michelle] I thought
he'd think I was crazy.

1212
01:05:17,580 --> 01:05:18,497
[laughs nervously]

1213
01:05:19,165 --> 01:05:20,833
But he didn't. [sobs]

1214
01:05:20,917 --> 01:05:22,919
[poignant music playing]

1215
01:05:23,461 --> 01:05:24,754
He believed me.

1216
01:05:27,548 --> 01:05:30,009
Just-- I felt so much relief.

1217
01:05:34,972 --> 01:05:37,350
And for the very first time,

1218
01:05:37,433 --> 01:05:39,435
I felt like I had

1219
01:05:40,728 --> 01:05:42,980
flipped the script on Ian.

1220
01:05:43,689 --> 01:05:45,691
And suddenly,

1221
01:05:46,901 --> 01:05:49,904
I was actually the one coming after him.

1222
01:05:50,404 --> 01:05:51,989
[tense music playing]

1223
01:05:52,073 --> 01:05:58,621
We realized the two religious emails
that she sent Ian are important.

1224
01:05:58,704 --> 01:06:04,502
Because we suspected Ian seizes on those
to create the Lilith account

1225
01:06:04,585 --> 01:06:07,171
and to create
this other religious language.

1226
01:06:08,547 --> 01:06:11,801
He mimics her when he writes these.

1227
01:06:11,884 --> 01:06:14,178
And this is evidence that points to Ian,

1228
01:06:14,261 --> 01:06:15,471
not Angela.

1229
01:06:18,015 --> 01:06:21,352
At this point, we were starting to suspect

1230
01:06:21,435 --> 01:06:24,772
that Angela might have
only been a passenger.

1231
01:06:25,398 --> 01:06:27,400
And that this was Ian's scheme.

1232
01:06:27,483 --> 01:06:29,944
[ominous tone plays]

1233
01:06:31,821 --> 01:06:33,823
[suspenseful music playing]

1234
01:06:33,906 --> 01:06:36,826
{\an8}It's important that
we find additional evidence

1235
01:06:36,909 --> 01:06:39,245
{\an8}to support this new theory

1236
01:06:39,328 --> 01:06:42,790
that we had
a Deputy United States Marshal, Ian Diaz,

1237
01:06:43,290 --> 01:06:46,210
who framed his ex-girlfriend,
Michelle Hadley,

1238
01:06:46,293 --> 01:06:48,087
for a crime she did not commit.

1239
01:06:50,506 --> 01:06:54,927
We first looked at the night
where Ian and Angela are reporting threats

1240
01:06:55,011 --> 01:06:59,473
that Lilith is sending
a rapist to the condo from Craigslist.

1241
01:06:59,974 --> 01:07:03,394
It is one of the most significant events
during this scheme.

1242
01:07:03,477 --> 01:07:06,147
She's stating that she's going to
have this guy come over.

1243
01:07:06,230 --> 01:07:10,484
She'll give him the address, and come over
and rape her and beat her, right?

1244
01:07:12,069 --> 01:07:15,948
[Jason] So it was important for us
to find the man on Craigslist, Rick,

1245
01:07:16,032 --> 01:07:19,869
because not only was he lured
to the condo under false pretenses,

1246
01:07:20,786 --> 01:07:25,875
he may give us information we didn't have
about what happened that night.

1247
01:07:25,958 --> 01:07:27,835
[suspenseful music continues]

1248
01:07:27,918 --> 01:07:31,380
So it took a little bit of sleuthing
to find Rick,

1249
01:07:31,464 --> 01:07:33,924
but we finally tracked him down.

1250
01:07:37,344 --> 01:07:38,345
[music fades]

1251
01:07:38,429 --> 01:07:40,514
[woman on radio]
<i>Firefighters in Southern California</i>

1252
01:07:40,598 --> 01:07:42,767
<i>are battling a wildfire</i>
<i>that's threatening…</i>

1253
01:07:42,850 --> 01:07:46,896
[Rick] <i>I want to be anonymous</i>
<i>because I don't want to be known</i>

1254
01:07:46,979 --> 01:07:50,191
<i>for my sexual fantasies.</i>

1255
01:07:50,274 --> 01:07:52,068
[woman] <i>Saturday,</i>
<i>Los Angeles fire officials…</i>

1256
01:07:52,151 --> 01:07:56,113
[Rick] <i>Because I am a single parent</i>
<i>and I didn't want to date at that point,</i>

1257
01:07:56,197 --> 01:08:00,659
<i>I was on the Craigslist meeting people</i>
<i>for casual encounters.</i>

1258
01:08:00,743 --> 01:08:02,536
[woman continues indistinctly on radio]

1259
01:08:03,162 --> 01:08:07,333
[Rick] <i>A rape fantasy, it's actually</i>
<i>a very popular fantasy, I would say.</i>

1260
01:08:07,416 --> 01:08:09,251
[pensive music playing]

1261
01:08:10,461 --> 01:08:13,380
<i>So I placed an ad on the Craigslist,</i>
<i>and it said,</i>

1262
01:08:13,464 --> 01:08:18,594
<i>"I am looking for women who have fantasies</i>
<i>about being raped or forced to perform."</i>

1263
01:08:19,512 --> 01:08:23,140
<i>I get this message from Lilithistruth.</i>

1264
01:08:23,224 --> 01:08:24,683
<i>Her reply stood out</i>

1265
01:08:24,767 --> 01:08:27,436
<i>because she seemed very eager,</i>

1266
01:08:27,520 --> 01:08:30,189
<i>almost desperate, to get this done.</i>

1267
01:08:30,940 --> 01:08:32,358
<i>I thought it was a bit odd,</i>

1268
01:08:32,441 --> 01:08:36,320
<i>so I figured</i>
<i>I'll get her on the phone to voice verify,</i>

1269
01:08:36,403 --> 01:08:38,739
<i>just to make sure that this is real.</i>

1270
01:08:40,574 --> 01:08:42,201
When I view the body cam footage,

1271
01:08:42,284 --> 01:08:46,789
there were a few things that struck me
about what was happening that night.

1272
01:08:46,872 --> 01:08:47,915
[pensive music continues]

1273
01:08:47,998 --> 01:08:52,878
The first is that Ian is able to identify

1274
01:08:53,546 --> 01:08:58,509
and communicate… with Rick on Craigslist.

1275
01:08:58,592 --> 01:09:02,429
[Ian] I'm trying to act like a girl,
and I ask him, "What's your number…"

1276
01:09:02,513 --> 01:09:06,475
[Jason] When our digital forensics team
looked on his computer,

1277
01:09:06,559 --> 01:09:11,897
there was no evidence of Ian going
to 40 or 50 different rape fantasy posts

1278
01:09:11,981 --> 01:09:13,440
to find Rick.

1279
01:09:13,524 --> 01:09:15,109
He hits the first pitch,

1280
01:09:15,192 --> 01:09:17,361
and he gets Rick directly.

1281
01:09:17,444 --> 01:09:22,449
The odds of that are just impossible.
This is like a million to one shot.

1282
01:09:23,659 --> 01:09:26,537
And then in his laptop backups,

1283
01:09:26,620 --> 01:09:30,666
we found Ian using
his personal email account

1284
01:09:30,749 --> 01:09:34,461
to jump right in
to this conversation thread

1285
01:09:34,545 --> 01:09:37,131
that Rick was having with Lilith

1286
01:09:37,214 --> 01:09:38,591
without missing a beat.

1287
01:09:39,091 --> 01:09:41,802
Such that Rick thinks
he's communicating with the same person.

1288
01:09:41,886 --> 01:09:43,179
[pensive music continues]

1289
01:09:43,262 --> 01:09:44,513
Ian asks,

1290
01:09:44,597 --> 01:09:47,558
"Are you headed to my place
in Anaheim tonight?"

1291
01:09:50,269 --> 01:09:52,354
Now, that certainly begs the question,

1292
01:09:52,438 --> 01:09:56,859
how did he know that Rick was coming
to the condo in Anaheim that night?

1293
01:09:57,359 --> 01:10:01,739
The only conclusion
is that Ian himself had responded

1294
01:10:01,822 --> 01:10:07,286
to the Craigslist fantasy rape ad
using the Lilithistruth email.

1295
01:10:07,369 --> 01:10:12,291
This is compelling evidence
Ian Diaz was running the scheme.

1296
01:10:15,294 --> 01:10:17,171
[Rick] <i>So when I got this message,</i>

1297
01:10:17,254 --> 01:10:20,758
<i>I replied, "I can,</i>
<i>but I need you to voice verify."</i>

1298
01:10:21,467 --> 01:10:24,762
[Jason] And now it's Angela Diaz,
pretending to be Lilith,

1299
01:10:24,845 --> 01:10:27,181
who actually voice verifies.

1300
01:10:27,264 --> 01:10:28,515
[Angela] <i>Hi, Rick, this is Lili.</i>

1301
01:10:28,599 --> 01:10:31,477
<i>I just wanted to confirm</i>
<i>tonight at 8 o'clock.</i>

1302
01:10:31,560 --> 01:10:32,770
<i>I'll see you then.</i>

1303
01:10:33,979 --> 01:10:35,147
[Rick] <i>I heard it was a woman,</i>

1304
01:10:35,231 --> 01:10:38,108
<i>so I said, "Well, okay, I'm going to</i>
<i>go down there and get this done."</i>

1305
01:10:38,192 --> 01:10:40,236
[pensive music continues]

1306
01:10:40,319 --> 01:10:42,071
[Jason] Something else
that jumped out to me.

1307
01:10:42,154 --> 01:10:45,074
While Angie is calling
Anaheim Police Department

1308
01:10:45,157 --> 01:10:47,910
and reporting that
Michelle Hadley is sending a rapist,

1309
01:10:48,702 --> 01:10:52,122
Ian is actively encouraging him
to come to the house.

1310
01:10:52,665 --> 01:10:55,668
[pensive music continues]

1311
01:11:00,047 --> 01:11:01,924
[Ian] My idea was, yes,

1312
01:11:02,007 --> 01:11:05,594
I had her go out there
and open the gate a bit so it'd be open.

1313
01:11:05,678 --> 01:11:08,472
I was hoping he'd come up.
I wasn't gonna rough him up or something.

1314
01:11:08,555 --> 01:11:10,266
I was just gonna say, "Just have a seat."

1315
01:11:10,349 --> 01:11:13,060
'Cause I knew you were coming,
and I was just gonna detain him.

1316
01:11:13,143 --> 01:11:17,064
Anyone who's worried that
a potential rapist is coming to your house

1317
01:11:17,147 --> 01:11:19,108
doesn't encourage them
to come to the house,

1318
01:11:19,191 --> 01:11:21,819
and then unlock the door,
and then unlock the gate.

1319
01:11:23,153 --> 01:11:24,280
But in this case,

1320
01:11:24,363 --> 01:11:29,076
it's clear Ian and Angela are doing it
to bring Rick to the condo

1321
01:11:29,159 --> 01:11:31,578
because they wanted
to frame Michelle Hadley.

1322
01:11:33,372 --> 01:11:35,332
{\an8}In his police interview,

1323
01:11:35,416 --> 01:11:39,044
Ian laid this all at Angela's doorstep.

1324
01:11:39,128 --> 01:11:41,505
[Ian] I can't believe
this is happening. [sighs]

1325
01:11:42,172 --> 01:11:43,716
I feel like a fucking idiot.

1326
01:11:44,216 --> 01:11:46,260
[Cunah] Who do you think's responsible?

1327
01:11:47,886 --> 01:11:49,430
I think Angela did it all.

1328
01:11:50,097 --> 01:11:54,393
Ian wants to suggest that all of this
happened right under his nose.

1329
01:11:54,476 --> 01:11:58,522
[Ian] It seems like I've been sleeping
with the enemy the entire time.

1330
01:11:59,815 --> 01:12:02,443
But it's clear watching
the body cam footage,

1331
01:12:02,943 --> 01:12:05,154
looking at the digital evidence…

1332
01:12:07,573 --> 01:12:10,159
and upon interviewing Rick,

1333
01:12:10,242 --> 01:12:11,910
that this wasn't the case.

1334
01:12:11,994 --> 01:12:12,995
[music stops]

1335
01:12:13,078 --> 01:12:15,664
This is Ian pretending to be Michelle

1336
01:12:15,748 --> 01:12:19,626
pretending to be Angela
catfishing someone to the condo.

1337
01:12:19,710 --> 01:12:21,712
[unsettling music playing]

1338
01:12:22,796 --> 01:12:24,673
This is a very complicated case.

1339
01:12:25,257 --> 01:12:27,676
This could be confusing to a jury.

1340
01:12:28,510 --> 01:12:31,513
Who's impersonating whom,
pretending to be whom?

1341
01:12:32,348 --> 01:12:34,433
You know, I need to clear my head

1342
01:12:35,100 --> 01:12:38,520
to reflect on how the case
should be presented.

1343
01:12:40,647 --> 01:12:46,111
And I'm thinking, "Did Michelle Hadley
pose a real threat to Ian and Angela?"

1344
01:12:46,195 --> 01:12:47,613
Of course not.

1345
01:12:47,696 --> 01:12:51,909
But how did they persuade the Anaheim
Police Department to lock her up?

1346
01:12:53,118 --> 01:12:58,040
So we needed to prove to a jury
that Ian had misused his position

1347
01:12:58,123 --> 01:13:00,417
and manipulated
the Anaheim Police Department.

1348
01:13:04,963 --> 01:13:07,508
-[officer 1] Hello.
-Hi. Come on in. How are you?

1349
01:13:07,591 --> 01:13:10,511
Reviewing the body camera footage
over and over,

1350
01:13:10,594 --> 01:13:13,263
we began to figure out how that happened.

1351
01:13:14,348 --> 01:13:17,893
The pattern of the scheme
begins with what would be

1352
01:13:17,976 --> 01:13:21,313
an otherwise innocuous impersonation
of Michelle Hadley.

1353
01:13:21,397 --> 01:13:23,023
I got another email from her,

1354
01:13:23,107 --> 01:13:25,567
and I haven't opened and checked it
because I was like…

1355
01:13:25,651 --> 01:13:26,485
[officer 1] Okay.

1356
01:13:26,568 --> 01:13:30,155
Communications to Angela
that are somewhat threatening…

1357
01:13:30,239 --> 01:13:34,743
The last one we got from her
was late last night, and she said,

1358
01:13:34,827 --> 01:13:37,454
"You won't have a husband.
Your children won't have a father."

1359
01:13:37,538 --> 01:13:38,956
"I hope your punishment is swift."

1360
01:13:39,039 --> 01:13:41,708
"I love keeping you waiting
for what is next. Enjoy work tomorrow."

1361
01:13:41,792 --> 01:13:45,337
"I'm sure it will be a painfully
enjoyable experience. Michelle."

1362
01:13:45,421 --> 01:13:47,423
[Jason] But to the
Anaheim Police Department,

1363
01:13:47,506 --> 01:13:49,174
there was nothing they could do.

1364
01:13:49,258 --> 01:13:50,884
[officer 2] Okay, it's a criminal threat,

1365
01:13:50,968 --> 01:13:54,096
but you can't do anything
until she gets served.

1366
01:13:54,805 --> 01:13:57,474
So, restraining order,
and this is the proof of service.

1367
01:13:57,558 --> 01:13:58,392
[officer 1] Okay.

1368
01:13:59,351 --> 01:14:01,979
And then it slowly ratchets its way up

1369
01:14:02,062 --> 01:14:04,690
with grotesque pictures.

1370
01:14:04,773 --> 01:14:08,944
These emails have pictures
of decapitated people,

1371
01:14:09,445 --> 01:14:12,156
aborted fetuses, decapitated fetuses.

1372
01:14:12,239 --> 01:14:13,991
[Jason] But the Anaheim Police Department

1373
01:14:14,074 --> 01:14:16,660
are not really acting
when the threat level is low.

1374
01:14:16,743 --> 01:14:19,246
[female officer]
It's a misdemeanor, unfortunately.

1375
01:14:19,746 --> 01:14:23,041
So Ian and Angela
have to increase the threat level.

1376
01:14:23,125 --> 01:14:27,129
Now we're responding
to ads for rape fantasies.

1377
01:14:27,212 --> 01:14:29,214
[woman on phone]
<i>Anaheim Police, Dispatcher Scott.</i>

1378
01:14:29,298 --> 01:14:30,966
<i>Hi, my name is Angela Diaz,</i>

1379
01:14:31,049 --> 01:14:36,096
<i>and I have open cases with Anaheim PD</i>
<i>on a person named Michelle Hadley.</i>

1380
01:14:36,180 --> 01:14:38,098
<i>I've been receiving emails today from her</i>

1381
01:14:38,182 --> 01:14:41,477
<i>that she has somebody that's going to come</i>
<i>attack me and rape me.</i>

1382
01:14:42,394 --> 01:14:47,483
[Jason] Police arrive on scene because,
according to the call they've received,

1383
01:14:47,566 --> 01:14:49,818
there's someone there to commit a rape.

1384
01:14:49,902 --> 01:14:52,362
Ian can see that they're police officers,

1385
01:14:52,446 --> 01:14:56,366
and he is standing there
with his firearm out

1386
01:14:56,450 --> 01:15:01,663
to persuade the Anaheim Police Department
that the threat is so severe

1387
01:15:01,747 --> 01:15:04,833
that he has to be prepared
to use lethal force

1388
01:15:04,917 --> 01:15:06,752
to stop his wife from being attacked.

1389
01:15:06,835 --> 01:15:08,212
Just asking to get shot.

1390
01:15:08,295 --> 01:15:10,506
-Yeah.
-I would have shot him.

1391
01:15:10,589 --> 01:15:12,132
[Jason] This is playacting.

1392
01:15:12,216 --> 01:15:13,592
[tense, pensive music playing]

1393
01:15:13,675 --> 01:15:15,260
By wearing his badge,

1394
01:15:15,344 --> 01:15:17,471
and then by putting it on the table…

1395
01:15:17,554 --> 01:15:18,514
[Ian] So…

1396
01:15:19,890 --> 01:15:23,769
My name's Ian.
I'm a U.S. Marshal. Sorry, this is Angela.

1397
01:15:23,852 --> 01:15:26,188
…Ian is trying to show to them, like,

1398
01:15:26,271 --> 01:15:29,066
"I'm one of you,
and you should credit what I say."

1399
01:15:29,149 --> 01:15:30,817
[Ian] Had I not emailed him today,

1400
01:15:30,901 --> 01:15:33,445
she would have been raped
outside in the courtyard.

1401
01:15:33,529 --> 01:15:37,157
Now, trying to persuade them that,
"I've never seen anything like this."

1402
01:15:37,241 --> 01:15:41,703
That Michelle Hadley needs to be
in a padded room in cuffs.

1403
01:15:41,787 --> 01:15:45,290
She's chilling at her apartment right now,
